Smart Watch Application

Requirements:

-Testing
-OpenCV image Processing
-Implement Picture capturing

Bugs:

-Occasional really slow start-up
-Application doesn't start correctly and crashes
-Bluetooth doesn't always connect
-Bluetooth sometimes loses connection when watch sleeps

Performance/Memory Issues:

-Start-up is slow
-Videos are large
-Sensor data file is about 730 bytes per second (about 2.5 mb an hour)
-Bluetooth power consumption?

WARNING: If handler is used incorrectly memory leaks will occur.
leaks will occur when an accidental handler loop is made. To combat this,
make a weak reference to the handler or make it static